nde2.types

Class NDE2Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • nde2.types.NDE2Result
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Area, Boundary, Dataset, DataSetFamiliy, DataSetItem, DateRange, NDE2Unit, Period, Periodicity, Subject, Topic, VariableFamily

    public abstract class NDE2Result
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Base class for all types resulting from calls to NDE2 Discovery service. Here to declare that the results are Serializable, as well as provide methods of controlling the lifetime of a result.
    Author:
    filip

      • NDE2Result

        public NDE2Result(int daysToExpire)
        Set up this instance of an NDE2Result to be valid for a specified number of days. Note that this API at this stage does not do any timekeeping, but NDE2Result provides convenience methods for you to do timekeeping yourself.
        Parameters:
        daysToExpire - The number of days this NDE2Result should be valid for.
